{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cffbce9195","title":"毛主席在八届十一中全会上的的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fe55406577","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"cffbce9195"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","name":"无产阶级文化大革命参考资料（1966年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3a53bf7066","type":"paragraph","text":"在八届十一中全会上","index":0,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"0ba7a039b2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛丰席的讲话","index":1,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"08d95a43a6","type":"paragraph","text":"对犯融的同志要给他出路，要改正储，不要离为别人犯蜡靓就不许他改正膜。我们的政策是惩前些后治病救人，一看二帮，团粘-批部-—团精。我们这个党不是觉外无党，我们是党外有党，党内也有派，从来就是如此，这是正常现象。我们过去批都国民党，国民党党外无党，党内无派。有人就","index":2,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"d64d3636af","type":"paragraph","text":"“党外无党是帝王思想，党内无派千奇百怪。”我共产党也是这样，你党内无派？就是有。比如酰群众运动就有两派，不过是多少周题。如果不开这个会再搞儿个月我看事情就坏得多，所以我看这次会是开得好的，是有效果的。","index":3,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"31f726d82a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛王席和外国语学院学生王海装的谈话","index":4,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"7c5780d15a","type":"paragraph","text":"（王海著：团员，主席的经女，会在外语学院凭语专修科学习）","index":5,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"b81728178a","type":"paragraph","text":"王：我们学校的阶极斗争很尖，听发现了反动标蓄。还有用英文写，就在我们英帮系的黑板上。主席：他们写的什么反动标器？","index":6,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"6574763658","type":"paragraph","text":"王：我就知道一条，“蒋万岁”主席：英帮怎么毒？","index":7,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"13c67be8e1","type":"paragraph","text":"王Tong liue蒋。主席：还写了什么？","index":8,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"f6cb7c36c6","type":"paragraph","text":"王：别的不晓得。我就知道这一条。还是章会告我的。主席：好：他多写一些贴在外面，大家看一看。他杀人不杀人","index":9,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"dd6d3fed0f","type":"paragraph","text":"王：不知道杀人不杀人，如果查出来，我看要开除他，他去劳动改造主席：呵：只要他不杀人，不要开除，也不要他去劳动改造，他留在学校里继学习。你们可以开一","index":10,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"bf906f7c78","type":"paragraph","text":"个会，他融一酵蒋介石为什么好？蒋介石文做了那些好事。你们也可以一毒，蒋介石为什么不","index":11,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"1166d78825","type":"paragraph","text":"好，你们学校有多少人？","index":12,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"19c8090d8c","type":"paragraph","text":"王：大概有三千人其中包括教职具主席：你们三千人中周最好有七、几个蒋介石份子。","index":13,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"c3341787e9","type":"paragraph","text":"王，出了一个就不得了，还要七、八个，那还了得主席：我看你这个人啊看到一条反动标酷就紧张了。","index":14,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"7ddb63e6d6","type":"paragraph","text":"王：为什么要七、几个人主席：多儿个就可以树立对立面，可以作反面教具，只要他不杀人。","index":15,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"bc2f6545e1","type":"paragraph","text":"王：我们学校里其彻了阶路，这次招生百分之七十都是工人、贫下中农子弟，其他就是干部子弟、","index":16,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"5ad97d49e3","type":"paragraph","text":"烈属子弟等。主席：你们这个班有多少工农子弟？","index":17,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"32dfa528b3","type":"paragraph","text":"王，除了我之外还有两个干部子弟，其他都是工人食下中农子弟。他们表现都很好，我向他们学到很多","index":18,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"a362119333","type":"paragraph","text":"东西。主席：他们和你关系好不好，他们喜不喜欢和你接近","index":19,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"},{"id":"3939918cf8","type":"paragraph","text":"01","index":20,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195"}],"page":{"id":"0ba70855a8","publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"cffbce9195","start":11,"end":11}}}},"__N_SSG":true}